<view class='init'>
  <span bindtap='showModal'>
    <slot></slot>
  </span>
</view>

<ConfirmModal id="ConfirmModal" imageSrc=''  cancelText='知道了' showOk='{{false}}' bindCancel='hideModal'>
  <view class='wrap'>
    <view class='title'>
      <view>科目{{step == 1 ? '一' : '四'}} 模考须知</view>
    </view>
    <view class='content'>
      <view class='item'>
        <span class='label'>考试类型：</span>
        <span>小车-C1/C2/C3。</span>
      </view>
      <view class='item'>
        <span class='label'>考试标准：</span>
        <span>45分钟，{{step == 1 ? '100' : '50'}}题。</span>
      </view>
      <view class='item'>
        <span class='label'>合格标准：</span>
        <span>90分及格，满分100分。</span>
      </view>
      <view class='item'>
        <span class='label'>出题规则：</span>
        <span>根据公安局出题规则组卷。</span>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='tips'>
      <view>
        <span>规则：</span>模拟考试下不可修改答案，错一题扣{{step == 1 ? '1' : '2'}}分，错题累积超
        {{step == 1 ? '10' : '5'}}题则考试不通过，系统自动提醒交卷。
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>


</ConfirmModal>